In addition, <a2_0>extreme sports<a2_0/> such as sandboarding, skydiving and 4x4ing have become popular, and many cities have companies that provide tours.[citation needed] The most visited places include the capital city of <a3_0>Windhoek<a3_0/>, Caprivi Strip, Fish River Canyon, Sossusvlei, the Skeleton Coast Park, Sesriem, Etosha Pan and the <a4_0>coastal<a4_0/> towns of <b8_0>Swakopmund<b8_0/>, Walvis Bay and Lüderitz.
